content.text: Gatherine is a cafeteria worker at Enies Lobby.

Gatherine is a pale woman, with black hair tied into two pigtails in the back. She has light blue eyes, and red makeup on her cheeks and lips. She has a large chin and large cheeks. She wears a white button up shirt, with a pink skirt.
She only cares about men for their looks.
Before the Enies Lobby Arc, she and Jabra had a relationship, until she dumped him when Lucci returned to Enies Lobby, hoping that she could become his girlfriend.

elements.text: ↑  One Piece Manga and Anime — Vol. 40 Chapter 379 (p. 10) and Episode 266, Gatherine is mentioned by Fukurou.

↑  SBS One Piece Manga — Vol. 42, Fan question: Oda-sensei, I have a question. The waitress named Gatherine-san turned down Jabra. What kind of guys DOES she like? Or does she already have a boyfriend?
